           </plentry>                <plentry >                    <pt >gateway</pt>                    <pd >                        <p >is the default gateway</p>                    </pd>                </plentry>                <plentry >                    <pt >metric</pt>                    <pd >                        <p >is the cost of the route (the number of hops)</p>                    </pd>                </plentry>            </parml>            <p >To delete routes, use the following command.</p>            <codeblock ><systemoutput >~(keystone_admin)$ </systemoutput><userinput >system host-route-delete <varname >uuid</varname> <varname >ifname</varname> <varname >network</varname> <varname >prefix</varname> <varname >gateway</varname> <varname >metric</varname></userinput></codeblock>            <p >where <b >uuid</b> is the UUID of the route to be deleted.</p>            <p >To list existing routes, including their UUIDs, use the following command.</p>            <codeblock ><systemoutput >~(keystone_admin)$ </systemoutput><userinput >system host-route-list compute-0</userinput></codeblock>        </section>    </body></topic>